  "title": "Barista",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Assist in daily F&B operations of taking orders, serving, managing cashiering duties</li><li>Perform any duties assigned by the manager</li><li>Ensure cleanliness of premise, equipment and adhere to health, safety and sanitation guidelines at all times</li><li>Provide prompt and good customer service, informing customers of current store promotion</li><li>Able to multi task and familiarized with these areas:<br />Espresso Bar Station<br />POS Station<br />Waffle Station<br />Cold Beverage Station<br />Café Station (Bussing)<br />Back of House (Prep. Work)</li></ul><p><strong>Health and Safety Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Adhere to Compass Singapore HSE systems and procedures</li><li>Follow all Emergency Response plans on site</li><li>Follow procedures for identifying, assessing and controlling hazards and risks</li><li>Adhere to and maintain food handling standards and food safety plan at all times</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum GCE ‘N’ level and above or related certificates in the related position</li><li>At least 2 years’ experience working in F&B as Barista or similar field</li><li>Computer literate</li><li>Passion about coffee</li></ul>",
